Show HN: Alcove.xyz – A Nuzzle replacement using RSS
text:
I’ve been working on a little site to replace Nuzzle after Twitter acquired and shut it down last year. The basic idea is that you connect your Twitter account and receive a unique RSS feed that gives you all the links that would show up in your Twitter timeline. I mostly built it for myself but given all the Twitter drama, I figure there are people out there like me who want to escape the commentary, but still value the links people share.

Please give it a try! If you encounter bugs or want to give feedback, you can drop a comment here or message me on Twitter at @kdamica.
